tment to act as a physical supplier of marine petroleum products in the port area of fujairah the company services its customers in the ports of kingston montego bay and ocho rios jamaica it operates approximately two double hull tankers in jamaica the company operates approximately three double hull bunkering tankers in singapore the company trades and supplies marine petroleum products off the coast and in the port of vancouver the company operates approximately two double hull bunkering barges in the port of vancouver it operates over two double hull bunkering tankers in trinidad and tobagothe company is licensed to act as a physical supplier of marine petroleum products off the coast of morocco and in the port of tangermed the company serves this service center with its gibraltarbased bunkering tankers and operates a landbased storage facility in tangiers near the port of tangermed with approximately  cubic meters capacity the shell las palmas terminal occupies an area of approximately  square meters providing bunkering services for a range of ship operators primarily along various transatlantic seaborne trade routes the terminal includes a lubricants plant and dedicated landbased storage facilities with approximately  metric tons capacity as well as onsite blending facilities to mix all grades of fuel oils and distillates it operates over two double hull bunkering tankers in las palmas the company leases fuel storage facilities at balboa and cristobal located at each end of the panama canal with a capacity of approximately  cubic meters the company conducts bunkering operations in the united states east coast region and has approximately  cubic meters of leased tank storagethe company competes with world fuel services corporation chemoil corporation bp marine limited royal dutch shell plc marine products corp exxonmobil marine fuel cepsa gibraltar ltd and fujairah national bunkering co llc » full overview of anwn company address aegean marine petroleum network 