lly supplies and markets refined marine fuel and lubricants to ships in port and at sea as a physical supplier aegean marine petroleum purchase marine fuel from refineries major oil producers and other sources and resell and deliver these fuels using bunkering tankers to a broad base of end users aegean is a large oil and shipping company in greece and has a global presence in  markets including america canada mexico the united kingdom france belgium cyprus spain portugal italy denmark bulgaria russia serbia the netherlands romania turkey switzerland south africa jamaica trinidad and tobago ghana singapore morocco gibraltar fujairah cape verde panama the united arab emirates china india indonesia malaysia and the canary islandspage needed plus the company supplies the united states navy in the mediterranean seacitation needed and it is listed on the new york stock exchange shareholdersedit as of  december  list of shareholders with significant interests dimitris melissanidis  peter c georgiopoulos  senvest management llc  richard mashaal   west capital management lp  on  august  ampni announced that the company would buy back all the shares held by dimitris melissanidis for  per share founder and largest shareholder of the company for  stake see alsoedit greece portal energy portal companies portal energy in greece referencesedit  a b c d e f g h i j  annual report pdf aegean marine petroleum network inc  may  retrieved  january    aegean largest independent fuel supplier in the world  aegean inc archived  at the wayback machine  aegean marine petroleum network inc nyseanw  aegean marine petroleum network inc to repurchase  shares owned by dimitris melissanidis aegean marine petroleum network inc  august  retrieved  january   external linksedit official website retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleaegeanmarinepetroleumnetworkincoldid categories companies listed on the new york stock exchangeoil and gas companies of greeceshipping companies of greecehidden